<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroup-1">Accessibility</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Braille translation service<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled WC<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Induction loop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Text Relay<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Signing service available<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Wheelchair access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Step free access <span>(not answered)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent9f67b558436846b6ae4fc2d6c8aee966">
</div>
<p>A braille translation service and a signing service  is available on request.</p>
<p>Induction loop is available in some services.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroup-2">Accommodation</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Access to TV<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Internet access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Public telephone<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Family accommodation<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Mobile phones permitted<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Private rooms only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Single sex accommodation only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent9b25a65b9e6347cea4a82f0809ce1c69">
</div>
<p>Internet access is only available in the Rooftop Restaurant on A Level.</p>
<p>Mobile phones are only permitted in some areas.</p>
<p>Family accommodation is available in the Special Care Baby Unit.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroup-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Patient library<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Pharmacy<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContentbad135bab41a4426af07dcd5f323018f">
</div>
<p>There is a large car park, with dedicated disabled spaces.</p>
<p>The Rooftop Restaurant on A Level and Costa Coffee on C level offer food and drink. There is also a newsagents, Boots store and clothes shop on C level.</p>
<p>The Patient Library is on D level.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
